%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%202%2C400%20Killed%20In%20Afghanistan%20Quakes%2C%20Say%20Taliban%2C%20As%20Deaths%20Mount%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20than%202%2C400%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20earthquakes%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20the%20Taliban%20administration%20said%20on%20Sunday%2C%20in%20the%20deadliest%20tremors%20to%20rock%20the%20quake-prone%20mountainous%20country%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Saturday%20quakes%20in%20the%20west%20of%20the%20country%20hit%2035%20km%20(20%20miles)%20northwest%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Herat%2C%20with%20one%20of%206.3%20magnitude%2C%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20(USGS)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20among%20the%20world's%20deadliest%20quakes%20this%20year%2C%20after%20tremors%20in%20Turkey%20and%20Syria%20killed%20an%20estimated%2050%2C000%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJanan%20Sayeeq%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Disasters%2C%20said%20in%20a%20message%20to%20Reuters%20that%20the%20toll%20had%20risen%20to%202%2C445%20dead%2C%20but%20he%20revised%20down%20the%20number%20of%20injured%20to%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%202%2C000%26quot%3B.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%209%2C240%20people%20had%20been%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESayeeq%20also%20said%201%2C320%20houses%20had%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed.%20The%20death%20count%20spiked%20from%20500%20reported%20earlier%20on%20Sunday%20by%20the%20Red%20Crescent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETen%20rescue%20teams%20were%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20borders%20Iran%2C%20Sayeeq%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20dead%20had%20been%20brought%20to%20various%20hospitals%2C%20said%20a%20Herat%20health%20department%20official%20who%20identified%20himself%20as%20Dr%20Danish%2C%20adding%20most%20of%20them%20were%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBodies%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Btaken%20to%20several%20places%20-%20military%20bases%2C%20hospitals%26quot%3B%2C%20Danish%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeds%20were%20set%20up%20outside%20the%20main%20hospital%20in%20Herat%20to%20receive%20a%20flood%20of%20victims%2C%20photos%20on%20social%20media%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFood%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20medicine%2C%20clothes%20and%20tents%20were%20urgently%20needed%20for%20rescue%20and%20relief%2C%20Suhail%20Shaheen%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Taliban%20political%20office%20in%20Qatar%2C%20said%20in%20a%20message%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20medieval%20minarets%20of%20Herat%20sustained%20some%20damage%2C%20photographs%20on%20social%20media%20showed%2C%20with%20cracks%20visible%20and%20tiles%20fallen%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHemmed%20in%20by%20mountains%2C%20Afghanistan%20has%20a%20history%20of%20strong%20earthquakes%2C%20many%20in%20the%20rugged%20Hindu%20Kush%20region%20bordering%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeath%20count%20often%20rise%20when%20information%20comes%20in%20from%20more%20remote%20parts%20of%20a%20country%20where%20decades%20of%20war%20have%20left%20infrastructure%20in%20a%20shambles%2C%20and%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20difficult%20to%20organise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfghanistan's%20healthcare%20system%2C%20reliant%20almost%20entirely%20on%20foreign%20aid%2C%20has%20faced%20crippling%20cuts%20in%20the%20two%20years%20since%20the%20Taliban%20took%20over%20and%20much%20international%20assistance%2C%20which%20had%20formed%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20was%20halted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiplomats%20and%20aid%20officials%20say%20concerns%20over%20Taliban%20restrictions%20on%20women%20and%20competing%20global%20humanitarian%20crises%20are%20causing%20donors%20to%20pull%20back%20on%20financial%20support.%20The%20Islamist%20government%20has%20ordered%20most%20Afghan%20female%20aid%20staff%20not%20to%20work%2C%20although%20with%20exemptions%20in%20health%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20said%20it%20was%20likely%20to%20end%20its%20financial%20support%20for%2025%20Afghan%20hospitals%20because%20of%20funding%20constraints.%20It%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20if%20the%20Herat%20hospital%20was%20on%20that%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20quakes%20triggered%20panic%20in%20Herat%2C%20resident%20Naseema%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20left%20their%20houses%2C%20we%20all%20are%20on%20the%20streets%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%20text%20message%20to%20Reuters%20on%20Saturday%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20city%20was%20feeling%20aftershocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%20202%20public%20health%20facilities%20in%20Herat%20province%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20the%20major%20regional%20hospital%20where%20500%20casualties%20had%20been%20taken%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20said%20in%20a%20report%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20facilities%20are%20smaller%20basic%20health%20centres%20and%20logistical%20challenges%20were%20hindering%20operations%2C%20particularly%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20the%20WHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20remain%20ongoing%2C%20casualties%20in%20these%20areas%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20fully%20identified%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696803240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fp9t5636g_afghanistan-earthquake-reuters_120x90_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-2-400-killed-in-afghanistan-quakes-say-taliban-as-deaths-mount-4462721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%202%2C400%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20earthquakes%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20the%20Taliban%20administration%20said%20on%20Sunday%2C%20in%20the%20deadliest%20tremors%20to%20ro