n%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20have%20been%20displaced%20due%20to%20fighting%2C%20UNWRA%20says%2C%20after%20Hamas%20terrorists%20launched%20thousands%20of%20rockets%2C%20and%20stormed%20into%20Israel%20before%20dawn%20on%20Saturday%20in%20a%20series%20of%20devastating%20attacks%20on%20southern%20Israeli%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERetaliation%20was%20swift%20from%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20who%20launched%20air%20raids%20on%20the%20impoverished%20and%20densely-populated%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%202.3%20million%20people%20live%20crammed%20into%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%3A%20get%20out%20of%20there%20now%2C%20because%20we're%20about%20to%20act%20everywhere%20with%20all%20our%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20warned%20late%20Saturday%2C%20telling%20people%20to%20leave%20certain%20areas%20saying%20Hamas%20hideouts%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20reduced%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20two%20days%2C%20about%20600%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israel%20and%20at%20least%20370%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20from%20officials%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BUnbearable%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20classroom%2C%20women%20members%20of%20Sarsawi's%20family%20sat%20on%20sponge%20mattresses%20brought%20from%20their%20home%2C%20surrounded%20by%20cooking%20gas%2C%20canned%20food%2C%20and%20jumbled%20bags%20of%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmal%20Al-Sarsawi%2C%2037%2C%20said%20they%20were%20still%20in%20shock%2C%20after%20hearing%20rockets%20thudding%20into%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BWe%20gathered%20what%20we%20needed%20from%20the%20house%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20mother-of-five.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20they%20couldn't%20sleep%20all%20night%2C%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20calm%20their%20frightened%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quo