anies%2Fnews%2Fhccb-tamil-nadu-skill-development-corporation-to-train-5-000-youth-123100800966_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhccb-tamil-nadu-skill-development-corporation-to-train-5-000-youth-123100800966_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Al-Aqsa%20Mosque%20And%20A%20History%20Of%20Israel-Palestine%20Tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20barbaric%20attack%20launched%20by%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20terrorist%20group%2C%20and%20the%20retaliation%20by%20Israel%20has%20left%20nearly%201%2C000%20people%20dead.%20In%20the%20surprise%20attack%2C%20Hamas%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20launced%205%2C000%20rockets%20on%20Israel.%20The%20fighters%20of%20the%20terrorist%20group%20have%20also%20taken%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%20hostage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Hamas%2C%20this%20is%20the%20start%20of%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Deluge%2C%26quot%3B%20reported%20The%20Times%20Of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20Deif%2C%20military%20commander%20of%20the%20group%2C%20in%20a%20recorded%20message%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20the%20people%20are%20regaining%20their%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20Deif%20also%20stated%20that%20Hamas%20launched%20more%20than%205%2C000%20misiles%20on%20Israel.%20He%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20%26quot%3BPalestinians%20living%20in%20East%20Jerusalem%20to%20join%20the%20forces%20and%20expel%20the%20occupiers%20and%20demolish%20the%20walls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20so%20important%20in%20Islam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwhere-is-al-aqsa-mosque-why-is-it-so-important-islam-2023-04-05%2F%5C%22%3EAl-Aqsa%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20third%20holiest%20by%20the%20Muslims%2C%20after%20Mecca%20and%20Medina.%20The%20mosque%20is%20situated%20on%20a%20hill%20known%20to%20Jews%20as%20Har%20ha-Bayit%2C%20or%20Temple%20Mount%2C%20and%20to%20Muslims%20internationally%20as%20al-Haram%20al-Sharif%2C%20or%20The%20Noble%20Sanctuary.%20This%20place%20lies%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Jerusalem's%20Old%20City%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20the%20home%20to%20two%20Muslim%20holy%20places%20-%20the%20Dome%20of%20the%20Rock%20and%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Mosque%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Qibli%20Mosque%2C%20which%20was%20built%20in%20the%208th%20century%20AD%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20mosque's%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20overlooks%20the%20Western%20Wall%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sacred%20places%20of%20prayers%20for%20Jews.%20It%20is%20being%20said%20that%20the%20first%20temple%20was%20construsted%203%2C000%20years%20ago%20by%20biblical%20King%20Solomon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201967%2C%20during%20Middle%20East%20War%2C%20the%20site%20was%20captured%20by%20Israel.%20Later%2C%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bannexed%20it%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20adjoining%20parts%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20in%20a%20move%20not%20recognized%20internationally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Retuers%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20became%20focal%20point%20of%20Israeli-Palestinian%20tensions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-conflict-timeline.html%5C%22%3Econflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20related%20to%20the%20mosque%20has%20always%20triggered%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20clashes%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20led%20to%20a%2010-day-long%20war%20killing%20more%20than%20200%20Palestinians%20and%2010%20Isralies%2C%20reported%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20this%20year%2C%20Israel%20police%20officials%20got%20into%20a%20fight%20with%20Palestinians%20that%20led%20to%20a%20cross-border%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20The%20clash%20was%20reported%20hours%20after%20over%20350%20people%20were%20arrested%20and%20removed%20grom%20the%20compound%2C%20Reuters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Waqf%20staff%2C%20police%20had%20used%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20stun%20grenandes%20to%20evacuate%20the%20compound.%20It%20happened%20during%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael's%20raid%20into%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%2C%20its%20assault%20on%20worshippers%2C%20is%20a%20slap%20to%20recent%20US%20efforts%20which%20tried%20to%20create%20calm%20and%20stability%20during%20the%20month%20of%20Ramadan%2C%26quot%3B%20Nabil%20Abu%20Rudeineh%2C%20spokesman%20for%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696785960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Faq77s1ig_alaqsa-mosque_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-hamas-al-aqsa-mosque-and-a-history-of-israel-palestine-tensions-explained-4461757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20Hamas%2C%20the%20recent%20attack%20on%20Israel%20is%20the%20start%20of%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Deluge%2C%26quot%3B%20reported%20The%20Times%20Of%20Israel.Muhammad%20Deif%2C%20military%20commander%20of%20the%20group%2C%20in%20a%20recorded%20message%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20the%20people%20are%20regaining%20their%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rep%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-hamas-al-aqsa-mosque-and-a-history-of-israel-palestine-tensions-explained-4461757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amp