%2C%20National%20Conference%20won%2012%20while%20its%20ally%20Congress%20emerged%20victorious%20on%2010%20seats.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20independents%20managed%20to%20win%20two%20seats%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20NC%20and%20Congress%2C%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20had%20entered%20into%20a%20pre-poll%20pact%20to%20keep%20the%20BJP%20at%20bay.%20As%20per%20their%20power-sharing%20deal%2C%20both%20the%20parties%20would%20have%20equal%20share%20in%20the%20executive%20council%20of%20the%20Hill%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20parties%20termed%20the%20verdict%20as%20a%20rejection%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20August%205%2C%202019%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20NC%20vice-president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20the%20outcome%20is%20a%20resounding%20verdict%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20policies%20and%20and%20empathic%20rejection%20of%20what%20Union%20government%20did%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjknc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jknc%3C%2Fa%3E%20ends%20the%20day%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20LAHDC%20Kargil%20polls%20with%2012%20councillors.%20Together%20with%20the%20Congress%20with%20whom%20we%20shared%20seats%2C%20we%20will%20have%2021%20or%2022%20councillors%20(1%20seat%20is%20still%20being%20counted)%20out%20of%2026.%20This%20is%20a%20resounding%20verdict%20against%20the%20BJP%20%26amp%3B%20its%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(%40OmarAbdullah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOmarAbdullah%2Fstatus%2F1711040727755698626%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaji%20Asgar%20Ali%20Karbali%2C%20working%20president%20of%20Congress%20for%20Ladakh%20UT%2C%20said%20that%20BJP%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Kargil.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20message%20is%20clear%20that%20BJP%20and%20its%20policies%20are%20unacceptable%20to%20people%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20NC%20had%20projected%20the%20election%20as%20a%20referendum%20on%20the%20August%205%2C%202019%20decisions%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20departure%20from%20its%20trademark%20politics%20of%20Hindu%20versus%20Muslim%2C%20tried%20to%20play%20the%20Muslim%20card%2C%20given%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20demographic%20composition.%20Kargil%20is%20a%20Muslim-majority%20district%20and%20its%20inhabitants%20are%20mostly%20followers%20of%20the%20Shia%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20electoral%20battle%20in%20Kargil%20after%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganised%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20NC%20as%20the%20single-largest%20political%20party%20in%20the%20polls%20has%20once%20again%20indicated%20that%20Kargil%20is%20politically%20and%20psychologically%20closer%20to%20Kashmir%20than%20Jammu%20or%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Leh%20district%2C%20which%20had%20erupted%20with%20celebrations%20on%20the%20grant%20of%20UT%20status%20to%20Ladakh%20in%202019%2C%20the%20people%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Kargil%20had%20opposed%20the%20bifurcation%20move%20and%20observed%20a%20shutdown%20for%20several%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20people%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20joined%20hands%20to%20seek%20full-fledged%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20constitutional%20safeguards%20for%20natives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetback%20for%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20BJP%20improving%20its%20tally%20from%20one%20seat%20in%202018%20to%20two%20seats%20this