0over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20resolutely%20working%20against%20Iran's%20support%20for%20terrorism%2C%20for%20destabilizing%20actions%20in%20other%20countries.%20We've%20sanctioned%20more%20than%20400%20Iranian%20individuals%20and%20entities%20precisely%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20support%20that%20they've%20offered%20Hamas%20in%20the%20past.%20And%20it's%20something%20that%20we%20remain%20extremely%20vigilant%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20unknown%20number%20of%20Americans%20are%20among%20the%20hostages%2C%20the%20Israeli%20ambassador%20to%20the%20US%20also%20said%20today.%20The%20diplomat%2C%20Michael%20Herzog%2C%20was%20asked%20on%20CBS%20News%20if%20there%20were%20Americans%20among%20the%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20abducted%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20there%20are%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20tourists%20and%20other%20foreign%20nationals%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20the%20war%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel.%20Reports%20say%20hundreds%20including%20foreigners%20were%20killed%20at%20a%20peace-themed%20music%20festival%20near%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20when%20the%20Hamas%20group%20started%20their%20attack%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGun%20battles%20raged%20in%20towns%20and%20on%20highways%20as%20the%20Israeli%20army%20sought%20to%20secure%20desert%20regions%20near%20the%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20rescue%20hostages%20and%20evacuate%20all%20areas%20near%20Gaza%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20reach%20each%20and%20every%20community%20until%20we%20kill%20every%20terrorist%20in%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20military%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20a%20day%20after%20hundreds%20of%20Hamas%20fighters%20launched%20their%20shock%20offensive%20and%20surged%20into%20Israel%20using%20vehicles%2C%20boats%20and%20even%20motorised%20paragliders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20widespread%20shock%20and%20dismay%20in%20Israel%20after%20at%20least%20100%20citizens%20were%20captured%20by%20Hamas%20gunmen%20and%20abducted%20into%20Gaza%2C%20with%20images%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20of%20bloodied%20hostages%2C%20and%20distraught%20relatives%20pleading%20for%20the%20state%20to%20rescue%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20German%20woman%20was%20killed%20and%20her%20body%20was%20paraded%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck.%20At%20least%2018%2C000%20Indians%20are%20stranded%20in%20Israel%2C%20while%20Nepal%20said%2010%20of%20its%20students%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20AFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696782480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fnlvegbs_israel-palestine-conflct-afp_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseveral-americans-may-be-among-the-dead-and-hostages-in-israel-says-secretary-of-state-antony-blinken-4462338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20Americans%20may%20be%20among%20the%20dead%20and%20hostages%20taken%20by%20the%20Hamas%20group%20after%20its%20biggest%20ever%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20in%20a%20TV%20news%20show.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseveral-americans-may-be-among-the-dead-and-hostages-in-israel-says-secretary-of-state-antony-blinken-4462338%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseveral-americans-may-be-among-the-dead-and-hostages-in-israel-says-secretary-of-state-antony-blinken-4462338%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseveral-americans-may-be-among-the-dead-and-hostages-in-israel-says-secretary-of-state-antony-blinken-4462338%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ama