cleshow%2F104264376.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104264376.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESingham%20Again%20is%20being%20shot%20at%20Ramoji%20Film%20City%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar%20has%20reportedly%20joined%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20Ranveer%20Singh%20for%20the%20shoot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-joins-ajay-devgn-ranveer-singh-and-kareena-kapoor-khan-in-hyderabad-for-singham-again-shoot%2Farticleshow%2F104264376.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Israel-Gaza%20War%20-%20A%20Major%20Shock%20And%20A%20Few%20Lessons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20the%20world%20was%20not%20grappling%20with%20enough%20instability%2C%20the%20renewed%20conflagration%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestinians%20has%20added%20another%2C%20more%20dangerous%20layer%2C%20to%20the%20mix.%20And%20it's%20not%20the%20usual%20stuff%20even%20by%20the%20standards%20of%20the%20Middle%20East.%20This%20is%20being%20termed%20as%20Israel's%209%2F11%20moment%20-%20a%20moment%20that%20will%20redefine%20how%20Israel%20deals%20with%20its%20security%20challenges%20going%20forward%20and%20how%20various%20regional%20stakeholders%20recalibrate%20their%20strategies.%20It%20is%20a%20massive%20intelligence%20failure%20for%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20basked%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20having%20a%20mighty%20security%20apparatus.%20But%20beyond%20that%2C%20it%20is%20a%20shock%20to%20people%20who%20have%20somehow%20been%20lulled%20into%20believing%20that%20they%20had%20achieved%20a%20level%20of%20security%20that%20their%20adversaries%20would%20find%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20to%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20when%2050%20years%20after%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War's%20surprise%20assault%2C%20another%20attack%20was%20launched%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%2C%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20which%20Palestinian%20fighters%20entered%20southern%20Israel%20by%20sea%2C%20land%20and%20air%2C%20the%20confidence%20of%20a%20people%20who%20have%20learnt%20to%20live%20in%20a%20volatile%20neighborhood%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20shaken%20to%20the%20core.%20That%20it%20was%20unexpected%20makes%20the%20scale%20and%20scope%20of%20this%20attack%20and%20its%20impact%20of%20the%20Israeli%20psyche%20unprecedented.%20Israel's%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20said%20the%20country%20is%20going%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20and%20difficult%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20he%20said%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bforced%20on%20us%20by%20a%20murderous%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20launched%20from%20Gaza%2C%20which%20had%20been%20under%20the%20control%20of%20Hamas%20since%20the%20Israeli%20withdrawal%20in%202005.%20As%20Hamas%20fighters%20penetrated%20Israeli%20border%20posts%20and%20military%20bases%2C%20killing%20innocent%20civilians%20and%20making%20a%20public%20display%20of%20it%2C%20the%20audacity%20of%20a%20globally%20proscribed%20terror%20group%20wreaking%20havoc%20was%20on%20full%20display.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20the%20terrorists%20had%20a%20field%20day%2C%20seizing%20military%20vehicles%20and%20hostages.%20More%20than%2024%20hours%20later%20the%20Israeli%20military%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20at%20war...%20still%20completing%20efforts%20to%20take%20full%20control%20of%20Israeli%20territory%20and%20communities%20from%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%20In%20Israel%2C%20300%20civilians%20have%20been%20reported%20killed%20with%20dozens%20of%20Israelis%20having%20been%20taken%20hostage%2C%20while%20Israeli%20counter%20air%20attacks%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20at%20least%20313%20people%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20with%20almost%202%2C000%20wounded.%20This%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20as%20the%20region%20and%20the%20world%20brace%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20local%20level%2C%20this%20attack%20will%20push%20Israel%20to%20reassess%20its%20military%20strategy%20at%20its%20very%20foundation.%20Given%20the%20meticulous%20planning%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20Hamas%20is%20fully%20aware%20of%20what%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20from%20the%20Israeli%20side.%20As%20retaliatory%20strikes%20began%2C%20Hamas%20called%20on%20Palestinians%20and%20other%20Arabs%20to%20join%20the%20action%20to%20%26quot%3Bsweep%20away%20the%20%5BIsraeli%5D%20occupation.%26quot%3B%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20ordered%20a%20massive%20reinforcement%20of%20troops%20as%20fears%20of%20multiple%20fronts%20opening%20up%20remains%20a%20real%20possibility.%20Ground%20operations%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20needed%20to%20free%20hostages%20from%20Hamas%20and%20then%20to%20completely%20decimate%20the%20terror%20group%20as%20Israeli%20officials%20are%20suggesting.%20But%20herein%20lies%20the%20catch.%20Such%20a%20move%20would%20entail%20Israeli%20troops%20entering%20into%20an%20extremely%20difficult%20terrain%20of%20urban%20warfighting%20where%20Hamas%20fighters%20can%20easily%20hide%20among%20the%20civilian%20population.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20quagmire%20that%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%20has%20long%20tried%20to%20avoid%20and%20that's%20precisely%20what%20Hamas%20is%20aiming%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20will%20be%20under%20pressure%20domestically%20to%20launch%20a%20major%20offensive%20into%20Gaza%20and%20Hamas%20would%20be%20waiting%20for%20this%20to%20escalate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20local%20conflict.%20The%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%20is%20embedded%20in%20the%20wider%20regional%20faultlines.%20Hamas%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20Iran%20and%20the%20Lebanese%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20(also%20being%20backed%20by%20Iran)%20has%20already%20entered%20the%20fighting%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20behind%20strikes%20on%20Mount%20Dov%2C%20a%20tract%20of%20land%20claimed%20by%20Israel%2C%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%2C%20which%20Hezbollah%20made%20clear%20was%20carried%20out%20%26quot%3Bin%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%26quot%3B.%20Israel%20has%20struck%20back%20at%20Hezbollah%20in%20the%20JabalRus%20area.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20Israeli%20tourists%20being%20killed%20in%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar%20has%20underlined%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bholds%20Israel%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20ongoing%20escalation%20due%20to%20its%20ongoing%20violations%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20at%20the%20global%20level%20that%20some%20understanding%20of%20the%20present%20predicament%20can%20be%20found.%20With%20its%20audacious%20attacks%2C%20Hamas%20was%20not%20only%20trying%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20the%20key%20interlocutor%20in%20the%20Israel%20Palestine%20issue%2C%20it%20was%20also%20trying%20to%20derail%20the%20emerging%20US%20strategy%20towards%20the%20region.%20As%20the%20Biden%20administration%20pushed%20for%20a%20rapprochement%20between%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Israel%20in%20exchange%20for%20security%20guarantees%20and%20civilian%20nuclear%20technology%20to%20Riyadh%2C%20new%20strategic%20contours%20had%20begun%20to%20emerge%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20This%20pact%2C%20if%20finalised%2C%20would%20have%20marginalised%20Iran%20and%20Hamas%20in%20the%20region%20and%20so%20it%20was%20scuttled%20with%20a%20grand%20terror%20assault%20on%20Israel.%20Now%2C%20as%20Israel%20fights%20back%20against%20Hamas%20and%20other%20terror%20groups%2C%20the%20Saudis%20would%20find%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20go%20in%20for%20normalisation%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20for%20fear%20of%20public%20disapproval.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20significant%20lessons%20here%20for%20nation%20states%20like%20India%20trying%20to%20grapple%20with%20terrorism.%20Even%20as%20the%20world%20is%20focused%20on%20great%20power%20contestation%2C%20the%20potency%20of%20threat%20from%20pernicious%20non-state%20actors%20has%20only%20grown.%20Technological%20advancements%20are%20in%20some%20ways%20levelling%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20non-state%20actors%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20the%20support%20of%20states%20like%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%20Security%20apparatuses%20should%20avoid%20mirror%20imaging%20their%20biases%20on%20the%20adversaries%20and%20should%20always%20be%20thinking%20the%20unthinkable%20if%20they%20are%20to%20remain%20ahead%20of%20their%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20is%20a%20potent%20military%20machine%20and%20Israeli%20intelligence%20is%20among%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20Yet%2C%20the%20latest%20attack%20reveals%20the%20vulnerabilities%20of%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20to%20remain%20in%20non-stop%20war%20mode.%20If%20the%20aim%20of%20every%20war%20is%20to%20achieve%20political%20ends%2C%20then%20perhaps%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20Israel%20to%20not%20only%20reboot%20its%20war%20machinery%20and%20reestablish%20its%20deterrence%20but%20also%20rethink%20the%20political%20ends%20it%20wants%20to%20achieve%20through%20the%20instrumentality%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696777680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fknjeeo_israel_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-gaza-war-a-major-shock-and-a-few-lessons-4461852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20if%20the%20world%20was%20not%20grappling%20with%20enough%20instability%2C%20the%20renewed%20conflagration%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestinians%20has%20added%20another%2C%20more%20dangerous%20layer%2C%20to%20the%20mix.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-gaza-war-a-major-shock-and-a-few-lessons-4461852%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israelis%20Taken%20Hostage%20Were%20Ripped%20From%20Everyday%20Activities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoni%20Asher%20last%20spoke%20to%20his%20wife%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20when%20she%20called%20from%20her%20mother's%20home%20in%20southern%20Israel%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%20terrorists%20had%20infiltrated%20the%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20phone%20got%20disconnected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20last%20saw%20her%20later%20in%20the%20day%20-%20in%20a%20video%20circulating%20online.%20She%20and%20their%20daughters%2C%203%20and%205%20years%20old%2C%20were%20huddled%20with%20others%20on%20a%20flatbed%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20vehicle.%20Men%20with%20guns%20ushered%20them%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYoni%20Asher's%20wife%2C%20Doron%20Asher%20Katz%2C%2034%2C%20is%20one%20of%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20Israelis%20who%20have%20been%20captured%20and%20presumed%20to%20be%20held%20as%20hostages%20after%20an%20unprecedented%20invasion%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20of%20southern%20Israel%2C%20taking%20control%20for%20a%20time%20of%20multiple%20communities%20and%20at%20least%20two%20military%20camps%2C%20and%20killing%20hundreds.%20Videos%20posted%20online%20show%20armed%20men%20marching%20or%20dragging%20men%20and%20women%20through%20the%20streets%2C%20some%20elderly%2C%20some%20bloodied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20authorities%20have%20responded%20with%20force%20in%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20more%20than%20300%20people%20and%20bombing%20buildings.%20On%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20Israel%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20seven%20communities%20and%20an%20army%20camp%2C%20IDF%20spokesman%20Richard%20Hecht%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20many%20hostages%20have%20been%20taken.%20Hamas%20has%20said%20it%20was%20holding%20dozens%20of%20commanders%20and%20soldiers.%20Israeli%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20number%20was%20at%20least%20100%2C%20including%20elderly%20people%20and%20children.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20confirmed%20that%20hostages%20had%20been%20taken%20but%20wouldn't%20give%20a%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hostage%20taking%20has%20struck%20a%20particularly%20emotional%20nerve%20in%20Israel%20and%20makes%20the%20country's%20response%20more%20complicated%20-%20and%2C%20potentially%2C%20more%20deadly.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20reserve%20military%20spokesman%20Lt.%20Col.%20Jonathan%20Conricus%20told%20the%20BBC%2C%20and%20later%20reiterated%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstagram%20and%20other%20channels%20were%20flooded%20with%20faces%20of%20missing%20people%20and%20pleas%20for%20information.%20Many%20of%20those%20identified%20were%20young%20attendees%20of%20an%20outdoor%20desert%20rave.%20One%20of%20those%20attending%20was%20Almog%20Meir%20Jan%2C%20who%20at%20age%2021%20had%20recently%20finished%20his%20army%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20called%20my%20mother%20at%207%3A45%20a.m.%20and%20told%20her%20there%20were%20rockets%2C%20that%20they%20have%20started%20running%20and%20that%20he%20loves%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20sister%2C%20Geut%20Harari%2C%20said%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%20%26quot%3BSince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20identified%20him%2C%20alive%2C%20in%20a%20clip%20sent%20around%20on%20the%20Telegram%20messaging%20app.%20The%20footage%20showed%20young%20men%20illuminated%20by%20a%20bright%20light%2C%20cowering%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20some%20with%20their%20hands%20behind%20their%20back%20and%20others%20attempting%20to%20shield%20their%20faces%20from%20the%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20wars%20have%20been%20set%20off%20by%20abductions%20and%20killings%20of%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%20or%20civilians.%20In%202006%2C%20the%20capture%20of%20three%20soldiers%20-%20one%20in%20Gaza%2C%20two%20in%20Lebanon%20-%20ignited%20the%20deadly%20Second%20Lebanon%20War%20with%20the%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah.%20Eight%20years%20later%2C%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20of%20three%20Israeli%20teenagers%20in%20West%20Bank%20by%20Hamas%20gunmen%20led%20to%20a%2050-day%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20In%202011%2C%20to%20free%20soldier%20Gilad%20Shalit%20from%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20freed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20several%20of%20whom%20went%20on%20to%20carry%20out%20deadly%20attacks%20against%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20many%20of%20those%20taken%20aren't%20soldiers%20but%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20family%20members%20say%20Israeli%20authorities%20haven't%20responded%20to%20calls%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20spoke%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Yoni%20Asher%20said%20at%20around%2011%20pm%2C%20after%2012%20hours%20of%20frantic%20calls%2C%20and%20after%20tracking%20his%20wife's%20phone%20to%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20contacted%20me.%20I%20called%20the%20police%2C%20I%20called%20the%20Home%20Front%20Command%2C%20the%20local%20councils.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20contacted%20German%20authorities%2C%20because%20his%20wife%20has%20German%20citizenship.%20So%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20Asher%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20and%20local%20television%20stations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20situation%2C%20hostages%20were%20being%20held%20for%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20in%20Be'eri%2C%20an%20Israeli%20kibbutz%20with%20a%20population%20of%20about%201%2C000%20located%20in%20the%20northwest%20Negev%20desert%20near%20the%20eastern%20border%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Tens%20of%20them%20at%20least%20were%20held%20hostage%20by%20armed%20militants%20at%20the%20settlement's%20common%20dining%20hall%20and%20later%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20woke%20up%20and%20realized%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%20Goni%20Godard%2C%2022%2C%20pulled%20a%20bandana%20over%20his%20face%20and%20headed%20through%20Be'eri%20toward%20his%20parents'%20home.%20A%20man%20pointed%20a%20gun%20at%20him%20but%20didn't%20shoot%3B%20Godard%20thinks%20it's%20because%20with%20the%20bandana%2C%20they%20couldn't%20tell%20which%20side%20he%20was%20on.%20Walking%20through%20the%20kibbutz%2C%20he%20saw%20bullet-laden%20bodies%20in%20the%20streets%20before%20coming%20to%20the%20place%20that%20used%20to%20be%20the%20home%20of%20his%20parents%2C%20Many%20Godard%2C%2070%2C%20and%20Ayelet%20Godard%2C%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20burned%20and%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20through%20sobs.%20They%20weren't%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20hid%20in%20the%20home%20until%204%20pm%20when%20the%20Israeli%20military%20arrived.%20He's%20still%20looking%20for%20his%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696776360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjk539d18_israel-palestine-war_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraelis-taken-hostage-were-ripped-from-everyday-activities-4462177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yoni%20Asher%20last%20spoke%20to%20his%20wife%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20when%20she%20called%20from%20her%20mother's%20home%20in%20southern%20Israel%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%2