%20Adviser%2C%20Doval%20led%20the%20discussions%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20the%20Chinese.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20discussions%20on%20the%20disputed%20nature%20of%20borders%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20Arunachal%20as%20well%20as%20a%20few%20other%20states.%20No%20doubt%20the%20Special%20Cell%20is%20hot%20footing%20it%20to%20his%20office%20right%20now%2C%20handcuffs%20at%20the%20ready.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%20Terror%20FIR%20Against%20NewsClick%20Puts%20Lawyers%20in%20Crosshairs%2C%20Names%20Chinese%20Firms%20Xiaomi%2C%20Vivo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoval%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20not%20the%20lone%20figure%20in%20the%20cabinet%20that%20would%20fall%20under%20the%20Special%20Cell%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20cartographic%20terrorism%20as%20a%20tinkering%20with%20maps.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20things%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20did%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20was%20to%20finalise%20the%20border%20with%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20blocking%20it%20for%20years%20with%20much%20frothing%20at%20the%20mouth%20by%20the%20late%2C%20unlamented%20Arun%20Jaitley.%20Does%20this%20mean%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20cabinet%2C%20and%20much%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20are%20all%20guilty%20of%20cartographic%20terrorism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20issue%20does%20not%20stop%20with%20Indians%2C%20since%20the%20Special%20Cell%20has%20said%20that%20all%20such%20tinkering%20is%20because%20of%20the%20propaganda%20arm%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20(CPC).%20Sadly%2C%20we%20now%20discover%20that%20Encyclopaedia%20Brittanica%20%E2%80%93%20which%20notes%20that%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca