al%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENobody%20expects%20them%20to%20part%20with%20their%20money.%20But%2C%20like%20the%20great%20West%20Indian%2C%20Michael%20Holding%20observed%2C%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfun%20and%20games%E2%80%9D%2C%20celebrities%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20use%20their%20privileged%20position%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20laurels%20won%20but%20what%20you%20give%20back%20to%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoseph%20Campbell%20put%20it%20best%20with%20his%20simple%20but%20profound%20assertion%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20hero%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20given%20his%20or%20her%20life%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20oneself%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20celebrity%20has%20generally%20been%20reticent%2C%20if%20not%20downright%20uncaring%20of%20his%20social%20responsibilities.%20I%20had%20a%20theory%2C%20now%20dented%20by%20Mane%2C%20that%20the%20poorer%20a%20nation%2C%20the%20more%20solipsistic%20and%20self-seeking%20are%20its%20rich%20and%20famous%2C%20possibly%20because%20of%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20insecurity.%20Amid%20conspicuous%20and%20widespread%20deprivation%2C%20our%20celebrities%20tend%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20misery%20by%20bolting%20their%20ivory%20tower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20celebrities%20wield%20incredible%20social%20power.%20With%20millions%20of%20devotees%20hanging%20on%20to%20their%20every%20word%2C%20they%20are%20up%20there%20with%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leading%20opinion-makers.%20They%20can%20invigorate%20social%20justice%20campaigns%20with%20the%20power%20of%20their%20voices.%20Regrettably%2C%20most%20of%20them%20are%20self-obsessive.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Tendulkar.%20The%20greatest%20run%20getter%20in%20history%2C%20arguably%20the%20richest%20cricketer%2C%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20Sachin%20has%20exploited%20his%20stardom%20solely%20for%20hawking%20merchandise%20and%20for%20other%20less%20honourable%20purposes.%20He%20sought%20and%20obtained%20a%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20customs%20duty%20exemption%20on%20the%20Ferrari%20presented%20to%20him%20by%20Michael%20Schumacher%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ferrari%20company.%20More%20controversially%2C%20he%20allegedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fdrdo-officer-files-cbi-complaint-on-sanjay-narang-resort-sachin-tendulkar-denies-economic-interest%2Farticleshow%2F53291570.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etried%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20procurer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20his%20hotelier%20crony%20who%20had%20illegally%20encroached%20army%20cantonment%20land%2C%20but%20the%20then%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20Manohar%20Parrikar%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20play%20ball.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Sachin%20goes%20missing%20when%20it%20matters.%20He%20remained%20silent%20when%20the%20female%20wrestlers%20protesting%20sexual%20harassment%20sought%20his%20backing%2C%20and%20he%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20his%20former%20teammate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-jaffer-uttarakhand-coach-cricket-communalism%5C%22%3EWassim%20Jaffer%2C%20who%20was%20unjustly%20accused%20of%20communal%20bias%20by%20right-wing%20bigots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereas%20Anil%20Kumble%20showed%20character%20by%20coming%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Jaffer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-jaffer-uttarakhand-cricket-communal-good-muslim%5C%22%3EWasim%20Jaffer%20and%20the%20Futile%20Pursuit%20of%20Being%20a%20%E2%80%98Good%20Muslim%E2%80%99%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20charge%20that%20Sachin%20is%20indifferent%20to%20the%20social%20problems%20of%20the%20country%2C%20his%20apologists%20claim%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Capolitical%E2%80%9D.%20How%20then%20do%20they%20explain%20his%20government-tutored%20response%20to%20the%20tweets%20of%20Rihanna%20and%20Greta%20Thunberg%20in%20support%20of%20our%20farmers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnabashedly%20playing%20toady%20to%20this%20regime%2C%20Tendulkar%20used%20mighty%20words%2C%20calling%20on%20all%20Indians%20%E2%80%9Cto%20resist%20any%20threat%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20by%20external%20forces.%E2%80%9D%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20rich!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20two%20other%20mega%20superstars%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20shutting%20themselves%20off%20in%20their%20luxurious%20cocoons%2C%20ignoring%20the%20life%20and%20death%20problems%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20shrinking%20democratic%20space.%20They%20finally%20spoke%20up%20some%20months%20ago%20in%20Kolkata.%20Amitabh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famitabh-bachchan-and-shah-rukh-khan-speak-up-modestly-but-its-still-welcome%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520went%2520on%2520to%2520say%2Cjingoism%2520along%2520with%2520moral%2520policing%25E2%2580%25A6%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ementioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20current%20brand%20of%20historical%20couched%20in%20fictionalised%20jingoism%2C%20along%20with%20moral%20policing%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20about%20questions%20being%20raised%20on%20civil%20liberties%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20Khan%20talked%20of%20cinema%20as%20a%20medium%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20humanity%E2%80%99s%20intense%20capacity%20for%20compassion%2C%20unity%20and%20brotherhood.%E2%80%9D%20A%20trifle%2C%20pussyfooted%20and%20oblique%2C%20but%20as%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20a%20penny%20is%20better%20than%20none!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20experience%20I%20know%20that%20our%20women%20are%20infinitely%20smarter%20than%20men%20and%20made%20of%20sterner%20stuff.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Emonths-long%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20of%20our%20internationally%20renowned%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20led%20by%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20against%20continual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpictures-phone-location-other-evidence-show-brij-bhushan-allegedly-making-advances%5C%22%3Esexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20most%20courageous%20face-off%20by%20women%20anywhere%20against%20a%20repressive%2C%20hostile%20government%20that%20used%20every%20sordid%20means%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20their%20knees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20despite%20coercive%20police%20brutality%2C%20waves%20of%20officially%20sponsored%20vandalism%20of%20their%20protest%20site%2C%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%20and%20vicious%20slander%2C%20these%20indomitable%20women%20stood%20their%20ground%2C%20eventually%20forcing%20this%20regime%20to%20initiate%20legal%20action%20against%20one%20of%20its%20own.%20By%20throwing%20down%20the%20gauntlet%20against%20a%20deeply%20ingrained%2C%20rotten%20culture%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20they%20spoke%20up%20for%20all%20the%20voiceless%20girls%20who%20cannot%20protect%20themselves.%20Their%20groundbreaking%20protest%20has%20forged%20an%20indelible%20legacy%20that%20will%20inspire%20all%20women.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20bleak%20time%20when%20our%20freedoms%20are%20under%20attack%2C%20comparisons%20are%20inevitably%20drawn%20with%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20the%20Emergency.%20Of%20yesteryears%E2%80%99%20Bollywood%20stars%2C%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20who%20would%20have%20turned%20100%20on%20September%2025%20this%20year%2C%20was%20the%20lone%20celebrity%20with%20the%20spine%20and%20moral%20compass%20to%20publicly%20express%20his%20dissent%20in%20the%20dire%20period%20of%20the%20Emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsrk-i-hear-you-and-so-does-everyone-else%5C%22%3ESRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%20in%20appreciation%20of%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ogre%20in%20that%20fascist%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20Dev%20Anand%20flatly%20refused%2C%20describing%20his%20own%20audacity%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20call%20to%20conscience%E2%80%9D.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20his%20films%20were%20banned%20on%20TV%20and%20All%20India%20Radio%20proscribed%20any%20reference%20to%20his%20name.%20Unfazed%2C%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20of%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Jayprakash%20Narayan%2C%20he%20delivered%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20The%20evergreen%20screen%20idol%20was%2C%20in%20truth%2C%20a%20real-life%20hero!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20any%20discussion%20on%20our%20celebrity%20world%20would%20be%20incomplete%20if%20it%20does%20not%20include%20the%20celebrity%20nonpareil%20%E2%80%93%20our%20ace%20politician%20and%20multifaceted%20supreme%20leader.%20The%20consummate%20purveyor%20of%20illusions%20and%20dreams%2C%20he%20has%20become%20all%20things%20to%20his%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20fashion%20model%2C%20tear-jerking%20thespian%2C%20religious%20leader%2C%20historian%20and%20even%20war%20strategist.%20He%20has%20had%20an%20overpowering%20influence%20on%20our%20society%2C%20a%20power%20that%20is%20almost%20deific%20in%20the%20religious%20frenzy%20that%20he%20invokes%20in%20his%20Bhakts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20celebrities%20are%20to%20be%20ranked%20by%20the%20extent%20of%20their%20influence%20on%20society%20%E2%80%93%20for%20good%20or%20evil%20%E2%80%93%20then%20our%20supreme%20leader%20stands%20peerless%20at%20the%20pinnacle%2C%20the%20dominant%20personality%20of%20our%20time.%20He%20has%20artfully%20exploited%20the%20unthinking%20credulity%20of%20his%20people%20and%20the%20fragility%20of%20our%20democratic%20institutions%20to%20set%20himself%20up%20as%20the%20ultimate%20arbiter%20of%20our%20country%2C%20impacting%20our%20society%20in%C2%A0%20indelible%20ways.%20The%20nine-year%20saga%20of%20menacing%20majoritarianism%2C%20hare-brained%20schemes%20and%20pure%20malevolence%20has%20left%20us%20a%20splintered%20nation%20full%20of%20hatred%2C%20cruelty%20and%20rage.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20terrifying%20legacy%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696761309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08153339%2F1885944-modi-1547197401.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhen-celebrities-bow-down-to-the-regime%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfun%20and%20games%E2%80%9D%2C%20celebrities%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20use%20their%20privileged%20position%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A198%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhen-celebrities-bow-down-to-the-regime%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20clears%20appointments%20of%2012%20executive%20directors%20for%20state-owned%20banks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696759808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2F