rs%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20transport%20these%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20firmly%20believe%20that%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20is%20not%20just%20a%20privilege%20but%20a%20fundamental%20right%20that%20every%20citizen%20should%20enjoy%20without%20interruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20TOI%20quoted%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20association%20as%20saying.%20The%20association%20also%20added%20that%20a%20blanket%20ban%20in%20the%20entire%20state%2C%20even%20in%20those%20areas%20where%20there%20is%20no%20law%20and%20order%20problem%2C%20serves%20no%20purpose%20and%20infringes%20upon%20the%20basic%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens.%20Senapati%20is%20a%20district%20which%20borders%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protestors%20also%20gave%20an%20%E2%80%98ultimatum%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20lift%20the%20internet%20ban%20by%20Friday.%20Failing%20to%20do%20so%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20escalation%20of%20protest%2C%20the%20agitators%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20internet%20ban%20is%20among%20the%20longest%20ones%20imposed%20in%20an%20Indian%20state.%20While%20the%20state%20government%20continues%20to%20extend%20the%20ban%2C%20it%20has%20come%20under%20attack%20from%20various%20internet%20freedom%20activists%20for%20this%20move%20as%20they%20claimed%20that%20it%20created%20hurdles%20in%20free%20flow%20of%20information%20to%20uncover%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696750884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08131052%2FF7SQIIebEAAHp2K.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-150-trucks-stopped-some-destroyed-during-protest-against-ongoing-internet-shutdown%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20protest%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Senapati%20Students%20District%20Association.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-150-trucks