West%20Bengal%20Minister%20Firhad%20Hakim%20and%20TMC%20MLA%20Madan%20Mitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08120457%2FTMC-raids.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%209%3A30%20am%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20team%20of%20six%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20officials%2C%20accompanied%20by%20central%20forces%2C%20made%20an%20entry%20into%20the%20residence%20of%20West%20Bengal%20municipal%20minister%20and%20Kolkata%20mayor%20Firhad%20Hakim.%20Barricades%20were%20swiftly%20erected%20around%20the%20premises%2C%20completely%20restricting%20outsider%20access.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20raids%20are%20being%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20investigating%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20been%20conducting%20a%20raid%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Madan%20Mitra.%20Mitra%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20Kamarhati.%20The%20Kamarhati%20municipality%2C%20among%20others%2C%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%20for%20alleged%20corrupt%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20recently%20conducted%20a%20search%20at%20food%20minister%20Rathin%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20another%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20examination%20of%20the%20office%20of%20arrested%20agent%20Ayan%20Sil%2C%20who%20is%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20corruption%20in%20school%20teacher%20recruitment%2C%20the%20CBI%20claimed%20to%20have%20uncovered%20substantial%20information%20related%20to%20broader%20recruitment%20irregularities.%20Following%20the%20orders%20of%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20a%20formal%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%2C%20and%20an%20official%20investigation%20has%20been%20launched%20into%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20extensive%20probe%20encompasses%20various%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20including%20illicit%20recruitment%20within%20various%20municipalities%20and%20teacher%20appointments%2C%20and%20illegal%20activities%20such%20as%20cattle%2C%20coal%20and%20sand%20smuggling.%20The%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20alleges%20that%20these%20actions%20took%20place%20under%20the%20TMC%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20into%20Hakim%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20was%20reportedly%20based%20on%20intelligence%20provided%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20is%20actively%20investigating%20the%20corruption%20in%20the%20the%20Urban%20Development%20Department%20and%20had%20already%20conducted%20raid%20on%20the%20properties%20of%20senior%20office%20bearers%20multiple%20municipalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHakim%2C%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20TMC%20cabinet%20and%20a%20key%20leader%20of%20the%20party%2C%20has%20a%20been%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Public%20Works%20and%20Urban%20Development%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Calcutta%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20Justice%20Tapobrata%20Chakraborty%20and%20Justice%20Parthasarathy%20Chattopadhyay%20highlighted%20the%20corruption%20in%20municipalities%20and%20school%20teacher%20recruitment.%20This%20landmark%20judgment%2C%20delivered%20on%20June%2015%2C%20significantly%20altered%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20entire%20recruitment%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrregularities%20in%20recruitment%20has%20been%20a%20burning%20issue%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Former%20urban%20development%20minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Ashok%20Bhattacharya%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Municipal%20Service%20Commission%20was%20originally%20established%20during%20the%20left%20administration%20to%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20municipality%20recruitment.%20He%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20current%20practices%20deviate%20from%20this%20purpose%20and%20called%20for%20greater%20oversight%20of%20the%20appointment%20process%20and%20involvi